</ref>。1990年，二人因「創造UNIX作業系統和C程式設計語言」而獲得了[[IEEE|IEEE]]頒發的{{tsl|en|IEEE Richard W. Hamming Medal|IEEE漢明獎}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ieee.org/documents/hamming_rl.pdf |title=IEEE Richard W. Hamming Medal Recipients |publisher=[[电气电子工程师学会|IEEE]] |accessdate=2011-05-29 |archive-date=2015-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150612152243/http://www.ieee.org/documents/hamming_rl.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>，1997年獲[[计算机历史博物馆|计算机历史博物馆]]研究員獎<ref>{{cite web |title= Dennis Ritchie — CHM Fellow Award Winner |author= CHM |url= http://www.computerhistory.org/fellowawards/hall/bios/Dennis,Ritchie// |accessdate= 2015-03-30 |deadurl= yes |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20150403185444/http://www.computerhistory.org/fellowawards/hall/bios/Dennis,Ritchie/ |archivedate= 2015-04-03 }}</ref>，在1999年4月21日又共同獲得了由美國總統[[比尔·克林顿|比尔·克林顿]]頒發的{{tsl|en|National Medal of Technology and Innovation|美國國家技術與創新獎章}}<ref name="NationalMedalAnnouncement">{{cite web |url=http://www.bell-labs.com/news/1998/december/9/1.html |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2006-09-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060327052807/http://www.bell-labs.com/news/1998/december/9/1.html |archivedate=2006-03-27 }}</ref><ref name="NationalMedalPressRelease">{{cite web |url=http://www.bell-labs.com/news/1999/april/28/1.html |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2003-11-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20031011075017/http://www.bell-labs.com/news/1999/april/28/1.html |archivedate=2003-10-11 }}</ref>。

2005年，{{tsl|en|Industrial Research Institute|美国工业研究院}}授予丹尼斯·里奇{{tsl|en|IRI Achievement Award|IRI成就獎}}，以表彰他對計算機科學技術做出的貢獻，以及UNIX作業系統對社會的廣泛影響<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.alcatel-lucent.com/wps/portal/!ut/p/kcxml/04_Sj9SPykssy0xPLMnMz0vM0Y_QjzKLd4x3cg_SL8h2VAQAv8HY9g!!?LMSG_CABINET=Docs_and_Resource_Ctr&LMSG_CONTENT_FILE=News_Releases_LU_2005/LU_News_Article_005372.xml |title=Dennis Ritchie, Bell Labs Researcher and Co-Inventor of Unix, Receives 2005 Industrial Research Institute Achievement Award |publisher=Alcatel-Lucent Press Release |date=2005-11-15 |accessdate=2012-02-08 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140204000724/http://www3.alcatel-lucent.com/wps/portal/%21ut/p/kcxml/04_Sj9SPykssy0xPLMnMz0vM0Y_QjzKLd4x3cg_SL8h2VAQAv8HY9g%21%21?LMSG_CABINET=Docs_and_Resource_Ctr&LMSG_CONTENT_FILE=News_Releases_LU_2005%2FLU_News_Article_005372.xml |archivedate=2014-02-04 }}</ref>。

2011年，丹尼斯·里奇和肯·湯普遜二人共同獲得了[[日本国际奖|日本国际奖]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=/c/a/2011/01/24/BUTI1HDJSA.DTL#ixzz1C5LtXdf3|title=Ken Thompson, Dennis Ritchie win Japan Prize|first=Evangelista|last=Benny|publisher=San Francisco Chronicle|date=2011-01-25|accessdate=2020-12-15|archive-date=2012-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120310051008/http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=%2Fc%2Fa%2F2011%2F01%2F24%2FBUTI1HDJSA.DTL#ixzz1C5LtXdf3|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 逝世 ==
[[File:Dennis_Ritchie_(right)_Receiving_Japan_Prize.jpeg|thumb]]（左）和丹尼斯·里奇，2011年5月]]
2011年10月12日，里奇於新澤西州{{tsl|en|Berkeley Heights, New Jersey|伯克利·海茨镇}}的家中去世，享年70歲<ref name="NYTimes" />。去世的消息由他之前的同事[[羅勃·派克|羅勃·派克]]提供<ref name=BBC/><ref name=RobPike/>，但未指明具體的去世時間和原因<ref>{{Citation | author = Associated Press | title = Summary Box: Dennis Ritchie, pioneer in computer programming at Bell Labs, dies at 70 | newspaper = [[華盛頓郵報|The Washington Post]] | date = 2011-10-13 | url = http://www.washingtonpost.com/business/summary-box-dennis-ritchie-pioneer-in-computer-programming-at-bell-labs-dies-at-70/2011/10/13/gIQAFKC7hL_story.html | accessdate = 2011-10-14 | archive-date = 2018-12-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181224065622/https://www.washingtonpost.com/business/summary-box-dennis-ritchie-pioneer-in-computer-programming-at-bell-labs-dies-at-70/2011/10/13/gIQAFKC7hL_story.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。此前丹尼斯·里奇的健康狀況一直不佳，並且患有[[前列腺癌|前列腺癌]]和[[心臟病|心臟病]]<ref name="NYTimes" /><ref name="BBC" /><ref>{{cite web|last=Gallagher|first=Sean|title=Dennis Ritchie, Father of C and Co-Developer of Unix, Dies|url=http://www.wired.com/wiredenterprise/2011/10/dennis-ritchie/|publisher=[[连线|Wired]]|accessdate=2011-10-13|date=2011-10-13|archive-date=2012-01-27|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wired.com%2Fwiredenterprise%2F2011%2F10%2Fdennis-ritchie%2F&date=2012-01-27|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Binstock|first=Andrew|title=Dennis Ritchie, in Memoriam|url=http://drdobbs.com/cpp/231900742?cid=DDJ_nl_upd_2011-10-13_h|work=Dr. Dobb's Journal|publisher=Dr. Dobb's Journal|accessdate=2011-10-14|archive-date=2012-01-27|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdrdobbs.com%2Fcpp%2F231900742%3Fcid%3DDDJ_nl_upd_2011-10-13_h&date=2012-01-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

丹尼斯·里奇對電腦領域產生了深刻影響<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.extremetech.com/computing/102835-dennis-ritchie-creator-of-c-bids-goodbye-world | title = Dennis Ritchie, creator of C, bids "goodbye, world" | publisher = Extreme Tech | date = 2011-11-02 | accessdate = 2011-11-28 | author = David Cardinal | archive-date = 2012-01-28 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.extremetech.com%2Fcomputing%2F102835-dennis-ritchie-creator-of-c-bids-goodbye-world&date=2012-01-28 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="TheEconomist">{{cite news | url = http://www.economist.com/node/21536536 | title = Dennis Ritchie and John McCarthy: Dennis Ritchie and John McCarthy, machine whisperers, died on October 8th and 24th respectively, aged 70 and 84 | publisher = [[經濟學人|The Economist]] | date = 2011-11-05 | accessdate = 2011-11-28 | archive-date = 2012-01-28 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.economist.com%2Fnode%2F21536536&date=2012-01-28 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.newswise.com/articles/the-strange-birth-and-long-life-of-unix | title = The Strange Birth and Long Life of Unix | publisher = Newswise | date = 2011-11-23 | accessdate = 2011-11-28 | archive-date = 2012-01-28 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.newswise.com%2Farticles%2Fthe-strange-birth-and-long-life-of-unix&date=2012-01-28 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.ciol.com/News/News/News-Reports/The-forgotten-tech-luminaries/156641/0/ | title = The forgotten tech luminaries: The new generation of the digital age owe a part of their numeric souls to Dennis Ritchie and John McCarthy | website = Ciol.com | date = 2011-11-01 | accessdate = 2011-11-28 | author = Shyamanuja Das | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/6525iFqEA?url=http://www.ciol.com/News/News/News-Reports/The-forgotten-tech-luminaries/156641/0/ | archivedate = 2012-01-28 }}</ref>。在里奇去世之後，電腦歷史學家{{tsl|en|Paul E. Ceruzzi|保罗·茨露吉}}評價說：<ref>{{cite news |last=Langer |first=Emily |title=Dennis Ritchie, founder of Unix and C, dies at 70 |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/local/obituaries/dennis-ritchie-founder-of-unix-and-c-dies-at-70/2011/10/13/gIQAXsVXiL_story.html |accessdate=2011-11-03 |newspaper=Washington Post |date=2011-10-14 |archive-date=2012-01-28 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Flocal%2Fobituaries%2Fdennis-ritchie-founder-of-unix-and-c-dies-at-70%2F2011%2F10%2F13%2FgIQAXsVXiL_story.html&date=2012-01-28 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

{{quote|里奇的名字並不容易讓人察覺，也不為人熟知，但是……假如有一個能夠把電腦放大的顯微鏡，你會看到裡面到處都是他的貢獻。}}

他的同事[[布萊恩·柯林漢|布萊恩·柯林漢]]也接受了採訪，說里奇從未想過C語言能夠變得如此重要<ref name="ForbesKernighanInterview2011-11-04">{{cite news | url = http://forbesindia.com/interview/special/brian-kernighan-no-one-thought-c-would-become-so-big/29982/1 | title = No one thought 'C' would become so big: Brian Kernighan | publisher = Forbes India | date = 2011-11-04 | accessdate = 2011-11-28 | author = Shishir Prasad | archive-date = 2012-01-28 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http%3A%2F%2Fforbesindia.com%2Finterview%2Fspecial%2Fbrian-kernighan-no-one-thought-c-would-become-so-big%2F29982%2F1&date=2012-01-28 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。他告訴《[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]》，「丹尼斯創造的工具——以及它們的衍生品——現在正廣泛用於一切事物」<ref>{{cite news |author=Steve Lohroct |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2011/10/14/technology/dennis-ritchie-programming-trailblazer-dies-at-70.html?hp&_r=0 |title=Dennis Ritchie, 70, Dies, Programming Trailblazer |newspaper=[[纽约时报|The New York Times]] |date=2011-10-13 |accessdate=2016-11-14 |archive-date=2017-09-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170912060138/http://www.nytimes.com/2011/10/14/technology/dennis-ritchie-programming-trailblazer-dies-at-70.html?hp&_r=0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他還提醒讀者，C語言和UNIX在之後各種著名專案的開發中發揮了非常重要的作用，例如[[iPhone|iPhone]]<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.deccanherald.com/blog/?p=220 | title = Myths of Steve Jobs | publisher = Deccan Herald | date = 2011-11-28 | accessdate = 2011-11-28 | archive-date = 2012-01-28 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fblog%2F%3Fp%3D220&date=2012-01-28 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.thehindu.com/news/states/karnataka/article2622056.ece | title = The tale of three deeply different technologists | publisher = [[印度教徒報|The Hindu]] | date = 2011-11-14 | accessdate = 2011-11-28 | author = Subhajit Datta | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fstates%2Fkarnataka%2Farticle2622056.ece&date=2012-01-28 | archive-date = 2012-01-28 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。

有人將丹尼斯·里奇與[[史蒂夫·乔布斯|史蒂夫·乔布斯]]進行對比，試圖探究二人之中誰更重要，然後得出一條結論，「在過去四十年的技術革命裡，里奇起到了關鍵作用——包括蘋果公司想要用來創造財富的技術」<ref>{{cite web |last=Duncan |first=Geoff |url=http://www.digitaltrends.com/apple/was-dennis-ritchie-more-important-than-steve-jobs/ |title=Was Dennis Ritchie more important than Steve Jobs? |publisher=Digital Trends |date=2011-10-13 |accessdate=2016-11-14 |archive-date=2020-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201024071320/https://www.digitaltrends.com/apple/was-dennis-ritchie-more-important-than-steve-jobs/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。有人說「從另一方面講，丹尼斯·里奇發明了兩項關鍵的軟體技術，這種技術是直接或間接組成現在每一件電腦產品的[[DNA|DNA]]。它聽起來很瘋狂，可事實的確如此。」<ref>{{cite web |last=Perlow |first=Jason |url=http://www.zdnet.com/article/without-dennis-ritchie-there-would-be-no-jobs/ |title=Without Dennis Ritchie, there would be no Steve Jobs |website=ZDNet.com |date=2015-10-09 |accessdate=2016-11-14 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111205242/http://www.zdnet.com/article/without-dennis-ritchie-there-would-be-no-jobs/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>還有人評價道，「許多在計算機科學和相關領域的人都清楚，里奇的重要性體現在一切需要通過電腦實現的工作之中」<ref>{{cite web |url=https://techcrunch.com/2011/10/15/what-can-we-learn-from-dennis-ritchie/ |title=What Can We Learn From Dennis Ritchie? |website=TechCrunch.com |date=2011-10-15 |accessdate=2016-11-14 |archive-date=2020-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201210215223/https://techcrunch.com/2011/10/15/what-can-we-learn-from-dennis-ritchie/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

為紀念丹尼斯·里奇，[[Fedora_(作業系統)|Fedora]]的開發團隊將Fedora 16（發布於里奇去世一個月後）獻給他<ref name="F16Phoronix">{{cite web | url=https://www.phoronix.com/scan.php?page=news_item&px=MTAxMjg | title=Red Hat Releases Fedora 16 "Verne" | author=[[Phoronix|Phoronix]] | accessdate=2011-11-08 | archive-date=2020-12-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201210215221/https://www.phoronix.com/scan.php?page=news_item&px=MTAxMjg | dead-url=no }}</ref>，而[[FreeBSD|FreeBSD]]的開發團隊也將FreeBSD 9.0（發布於2012年1月12日）獻給他<ref name="FreeBSD">{{cite web |url=http://www.freebsd.org/releases/9.0R/announce.html |title=FreeBSD-9.0 Announcement |author=The FreeBSD project |accessdate=2012-01-12 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112015706/https://www.freebsd.org/releases/9.0R/announce.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

